| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1813 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02488e95-bd7b-54c9-bd6e-6238bc5df4f9"
